item.title: Miguel Angel Venero Yupanqui
item.description: Miguel Venero Yupanqui is a recent graduate in Computer Science at the University of Central Florida. Miguel completed his BSc. in Computer Science in December 2023. His research interests include Smart Mobility, Artificial Intelligence, Robotics, etc.
